high_descs: Turn right and approach the coffee maker.
Pick up the loaf of bread from the counter.
Turn around and go to the fridge.
Chill the bread and then pick it up again.
Go to the table in the corner to your left.
Put the bread on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold loaf of bread on the table.

high_descs: turn right and walk into the kitchen, keep walking until you reach the counter tops, turn right and face the counter top that has a loaf of bread on it
pick up the loaf of bread
turn right and walk until you face the black fridge
open the fridge, place the bread on the top shelf, close the door, wait, open the door, pick up the loaf of bread again
turn left, walk into the dining room, turn right and face the dining room table
put the loaf of bread on the table
anns.task_desc: pick up the loaf of bread, chill it briefly in the fridge, put it on the dining room table

high_descs: Turn right and begin walking across the room, then hang a right and walk over to the coffee machine, turn right to face the counter once there.
Pick up the loaf of bread off of the counter.
Turn around and begin walking across the room then hang a left and walk up to the fridge.
Put the loaf of bread in the fridge for a couple seconds to let it get cold, then take it out and close the fridge.
Turn left and walk over to the wall, then hang a right and walk over to the chair, once there turn right to face the round wooden table.
Place the chilled loaf of bread onto the round wooden table to the right of the apple.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled loaf of bread on the round wooden table.
